Blaine,

Start limbering up now!<grin> and warming up the VOM.

Start by cleaning all of the fuses and contacts well.
Clean all of the grounds everywhere.

Then see what you have.  Instrument lights might be a bad rheostat
in the lightswitch.

Cheers, dave

